flowchart TD
    A([Client Request]) --> B[API Gateway receives request]
    B --> C{Authenticate}
    C -- Invalid credentials --> D[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    C -- Valid --> E{Authorize}
    E -- Forbidden --> F[Return 403 Forbidden]
    E -- Allowed --> G{Rate limit check}
    G -- Quota exceeded --> H[Return 429 Too Many Requests]
    G -- Within quota --> I[Match route to upstream service]
    I --> J{Route found?}
    J -- No match --> K[Return 404 Not Found]
    J -- Matched --> L[Transform request headers and payload]
    L --> M[Proxy to upstream service]
    M --> N{Upstream response}
    N -- 5xx error --> O[Return 502 Bad Gateway]
    N -- Success --> P[Transform response]
    P --> Q([Return response to client])
